## Install gnparser

gnparser is required to use this package.

Installation instructions can be found at the [gnparser repo](https://gitlab.com/gogna/gnparser). 


## Install 

```{r eval=FALSE}
remotes::install_github("ropensci/rgnparser")
```

```{r}
library("rgnparser")
```
